diff.com/aloksin/oze.htm">link toview some of the images we were fortunate to see in Oze</a>. Many thanksto Alok for taking such great photos.</blockquote><hr><p>Please view the <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/page3.htm">HikingAdvice Page</a> to find out what to bring on our trips and extra informationregarding hiking in Japan.<blockquote>&nbsp;</blockquote><center><font size=-1><b>Home Page</b>| <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/nihongo.htm">Nihongo</a>|<a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/favorite_links.htm">FavoriteLinks</a>| <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/page1.htm">Hikes&amp; Photos</a></font> <font size=-1>| <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/page2.htm">SafetyPage for Walking</a></font> <font size=-1>| <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/page3.htm">HikingAdvice</a></font> <font size=-1>| <a href="http://www.geocities.com/Yosemite/Gorge/6108/old/contact_us.htm">ContactUs</a></font><p><img SRC="stod_bar.gif" height=23 width=520 align=BOTTOM></center><p><font size=-1>John Payne c/o TWMC</font><br><font size=-1><a href="mailto:john.payne@kyowa.co.jp">john.payne@kyowa.co.jp</a></font><br><font size=-1>Date Last Modified: 98/11/05</font><br><font size=-1>Tsukuba Walking &amp; Mountaineering Club</font><p><hr><br><img SRC="serv" height=1 width=1><!-- <SERVICE NAME="toto"> --><script LANGUAGE="javascript">window.open('http://geocities.yahoo.com/toto?s=76000022', '_geo_toto', 'width=515,height=125');</script><!-- </SERVICE> --></body></html>